      • isSvtValidationSuccess

        public boolean isSvtValidationSuccess()
        Is true if the SVT is valid and matches the signed document and the assigned signature. This is not an indication that the signature was successfully validated in the past. This is determined by the policy validation results carried in the SignatureClaims object.
        Returns:
        SVT validation success flag
